{"text_id":189570,"tokens":["In"," this"," research"," work",","," we"," investigate"," some"," aspects"," of"," measurement"," error"," in"," linear"," regression"," of"," astronomical"," data","."," The"," motivation"," for"," this"," research"," stems"," from"," the"," prevalence"," of"," measurement"," error"," in"," observational"," data",","," which"," can"," lead"," to"," misleading"," conclusions"," and"," inaccurate"," results","."," Our"," work"," aims"," to"," address"," this"," issue"," by"," examining"," the"," impact"," of"," measurement"," error"," on"," the"," regression"," coefficients"," and"," standard"," errors"," in"," linear"," regression"," models","."," ","\n\n","We"," begin"," by"," conducting"," a"," simulation"," study",","," where"," we"," generate"," data"," with"," varying"," levels"," of"," measurement"," error"," and"," examine"," the"," resulting"," regression"," coefficients"," and"," standard"," errors","."," We"," also"," investigate"," the"," effect"," of"," sample"," size"," and"," signal","-","to","-","noise"," ratio"," on"," the"," accuracy"," of"," the"," regression"," results","."," In"," addition",","," we"," apply"," our"," methods"," to"," a"," real","-","world"," astronomical"," data"," set"," and"," compare"," the"," results"," to"," those"," obtained"," from"," traditional"," regression"," techniques","."," ","\n\n","Our"," findings"," highlight"," the"," importance"," of"," accounting"," for"," measurement"," error"," in"," linear"," regression"," analysis"," of"," astronomical"," data","."," We"," demonstrate"," that"," ignoring"," measurement"," error"," can"," lead"," to"," biased"," estimates"," and"," incorrect"," inference",","," and"," that"," our"," proposed"," methods"," can"," improve"," the"," accuracy"," and"," reliability"," of"," regression"," results","."," Our"," work"," contributes"," to"," the"," development"," of"," statistical"," methods"," for"," handling"," measurement"," error"," in"," observational"," data",","," with"," potential"," applications"," in"," a"," wide"," range"," of"," scientific"," fields","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}